#- §5§lClue One: §0A warrior§0
§0looks to his 4§0
§0comrades with vigor in§0
§0his eyes. "This is our§0
§0first conquest! Let us§0
§0go!" The warrior holds§0
§0his sword high above§0
§0his head and the 4§0
§0others join in.§0

