§0iron golems are§0
§0blocking the entrance§0
§0to a bar. One heads§0
§0inside to buy a§0
§0standard beer. The§0
§0bartender says, "If§0
§0your friends stay out§0
§0there, it's gonna take§0
§0forever to get rid of§0
§0this beer!"§0

